those ancient, single-celled

00:01:38.010 --> 00:01:41.100 align:middle line:90%
creatures into oil.

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:43.900 align:middle line:90%


00:01:43.900 --> 00:01:48.070 align:middle line:84%
