01:09:32.270 --> 01:09:33.640 align:middle line:10%
And similarly, soy.

01:09:33.640 --> 01:09:35.890 align:middle line:10%
You can make a good
biodiesel from soy.

01:09:35.890 --> 01:09:37.390 align:middle line:10%
And there's a big
lobby behind it.

01:09:37.390 --> 01:09:40.240 align:middle line:84%
>> Most of the ethanol in
the US is made from corn.

01:09:40.240 --> 01:09:44.830 align:middle line:84%
And corn is grown in huge,
monocrop fields of tens

01:09:44.830 --> 01:09:47.620 align:middle line:84%
or even hundreds of
