01:10:33.100 --> 01:10:36.670 align:middle line:84%
it will be the largest ever,
about 8,500 square miles.

01:10:36.670 --> 01:10:39.850 align:middle line:84%
That's the size
of Massachusetts.

01:10:39.850 --> 01:10:43.900 align:middle line:84%
>> Ethanol from corn was grown
by large corporations that

01:10:43.900 --> 01:10:46.330 align:middle line:84%
